- Set concurrency limit at 10 subagents rather than 5: the SKILL.md targets an AI agent audience that can manage 10 concurrent subagents, and 5 would be overly conservative for typical batch sizes.
- Reword the mergedAt constraint rather than just appending: the original wording was actively misleading under the parallel model, so a rewrite was needed to avoid confusion.

